harmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/115411/', '', 'Pertuzumab, Cetuximab, Avelumab, Panitumumab, Obinutuzumab, Bevacizumab, Necitumumab, Dostarlimab, Ramucirumab, Atezolizumab, Amivantamab, More', 'Interferon alfa-n1, Oprelvekin, Elapegademase, Peginterferon alfa-2a, Interferon alfacon-1, Histamine, Aldesleukin, Pegademase, Interferon alfa-2b, Peginterferon alfa-2b, Glatiramer', 1767369485);
